121109 22:18:53	    2 Query	CREATE DEFINER = `root`@`` PROCEDURE `_Navicat_Temp_Stored_Proc`()
BEGIN

	DECLARE iSpawnNumVeh SMALLINT(3) DEFAULT 60;		
	
	CALL pCleanup();
	CALL pFixMaxNum;

	SELECT SUM(MaxNum) FROM object_classes INTO @iMaxNumTotal;
	IF (iSpawnNumVeh > @iMaxNumTotal) THEN
		SET iSpawnNumVeh = @iMaxNumTotal;
	END IF;

	WHILE (fGetVehCount() < iSpawnNumVeh) DO
		CALL pSpawn();
	END WHILE;

END

	DECLARE iSpawnNumVeh SMALLINT(3) DEFAULT 11;		
	
	CALL pCleanup();
	CALL pFixMaxNum;

	SELECT SUM(MaxNum) FROM object_classes INTO @iMaxNumTotal;
	IF (iSpawnNumVeh > @iMaxNumTotal) THEN
		SET iSpawnNumVeh = @iMaxNumTotal;
	END IF;

	WHILE (fGetVehCount() < iSpawnNumVeh) DO
		CALL pSpawn();
	END WHILE;

END

	CALL pFixMaxNum;
